{"tid":2412652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"布拉格總主教形容新冠病毒為「中国病毒」　中方表示強烈不滿","createTime":"2021-02-18T06:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T17:34:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":98,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab7079268cbefe95bacca8491dbaa33b53df1eb","tid":2412652,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:58:55.000Z","msg":"天主教布拉格總教區總主教杜卡，日前把新型冠狀病毒稱為「中國病毒」，並形容為被洩漏的「生物武器」，中國駐捷克大使館表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。中方表示，病毒溯源是複雜科學問題，不能用無端猜疑和蓄意歪曲代替科學研究，又指世衛專家已多次強調，新冠病毒「極不可能」源於實驗室洩漏，批評杜卡言論無視科學家意見，毫無事實根據，是不尊重科學和無端誣衊中國，敦促杜卡立即糾正錯誤，切實消除惡劣影響。<br />\n<br />\n捷克國防部早前亦指杜卡的言論缺乏證據，當地科學界人士早前亦批評，杜卡散佈虛假訊息，言論純屬誹謗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2379507/布拉格總主教形容新冠病毒為中國病毒-中方表示強烈不滿\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2379507%2F%E5%B8%83%E6%8B%89%E6%A0%BC%E7%B8%BD%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=c15d060f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2379507/布拉格總主教形容新冠病毒為中國病毒-中方表示強烈不滿</a>"},{"pid":"6c25f3379a6396d410217837ccab318ac985bb87","tid":2412652,"uid":28641,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n應該叫支那病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6220b2f72dd00c0ee58664aefadba18bee410871","tid":2412652,"uid":144626,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:00:48.000Z","msg":"望天主保祐你,取代方濟各呢件魔鬼做教宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9678298acce14f0b9bb207b5fa9c68d3228862","tid":2412652,"uid":25468,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:02:0